pool (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Kernel module: ChaCha20-Poly1305 AEAD, X25519 ECDH, ML-KEM-768 PQC,
    IP Protocol 253 transport, multicast peer discovery, built-in telemetry,
    atomic configuration with rollback, change journaling.
  * Userspace tools: poolctl, poold, pool_bridge, pool_migrate, pool_vault,
    pool_relay, pool_test, libpool_shim.so, pool_exporter.py.
  * Systemd integration: 5 service units with dependency ordering.
  * DKMS support: auto-rebuild on kernel upgrades.

 -- POOL Protocol Maintainers <pool-dev@example.com>  Sat, 15 Feb 2026 20:00:00 +0000
